Package: naabu
Version: 2.6.1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, golang, libcap
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/projectdiscovery/naabu
Description: Fast port scanner written in Go
 naabu is a fast port scanner designed for reconnaissance and
 network enumeration. It supports SYN, CONNECT, and UDP scans
 with high performance and low resource usage.
